# Threat Intelligence: Mobile

**Analysis Task**: Check if the SMS link is phishing or a legitimate bank notification.

**Threat Indicator**: SMS: 'Urgent! Your account is locked. Click http://phishy-site.com to verify.'

**Analysis Result**: Likely SMS-based phishing. Advise users not to click and to contact the bank through official channels.

**Threat Metadata**: {
  "threat_type": "mobile",
  "TTP": [
    "TA0001: Initial Access",
    "T1566: Phishing"
  ],
  "Kill_Chain_Stage": "Delivery",
  "CVSS": 5.7,
  "Threat_Actor": "Unknown",
  "Sector_Impact": [
    "Retail Banking"
  ],
  "IoCs": {
    "domains": [
      "phishy-site.com"
    ],
    "phone_numbers": [
      "+1-555-123-4567"
    ]
  }
}

# Threat Intelligence: Mobile

**Analysis Task**: Identify if this gaming application exhibits malicious adware behavior.

**Threat Indicator**: User complaints about excessive ads popping up and redirecting to unknown sites after installing a new mobile game.

**Analysis Result**: Indicators suggest adware infiltration. Remove the app and run mobile antivirus to clear adware residues.

**Threat Metadata**: {
  "threat_type": "mobile",
  "TTP": [
    "TA0005: Defense Evasion",
    "T1406: Obfuscated Files or Information"
  ],
  "Kill_Chain_Stage": "Installation",
  "CVSS": 4.2,
  "Threat_Actor": "Unknown",
  "Sector_Impact": [
    "Gaming Community"
  ],
  "IoCs": {
    "package_names": [
      "com.fakegaming.adware"
    ],
    "domains": [
      "random-ads.site"
    ],
    "permissions": [
      "INTERNET",
      "READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE"
    ]
  }
}

